'''Gaeriel''' was the fourth most popular baby name according to the [[HoloNet News/Legends|HoloNet News]] column, ''A Closer Look'', during the year [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]]

It was a common [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] [[Gender/Legends|female]] name and could also be spelled '''Gaerial''' or shortened to '''"Gaeri."''' Notable Gaeriels included:
*[[Gaeriel Capens]], musician
*[[Gaeriel Captison]], [[Prime Minister (Bakura)|Prime Minister]] of [[Bakura/Legends|Bakura]]

